title: AHS Apocalypse: A Rant and Finale Prediction
author: MaryGirl Moody
comment: The witches need their own spin off . Or give Michael his own show!
LMAOOOO what if season 9 is Apocalypse part 2 and season 10 is just like AHS: Hell

I totally LOVE American Horror Story. But, I also love how you told those, who take the show way too seriously and who have no sense of humor, to go fuck off! Lol. I can't stand people, who act like their theories about the show are frigging facts, instead of what they really are, which are simply guesses. Then, they'll even fight with those who happen to disagree with them.
I totally hate that I work tomorrow in Madison's hell. Y'all enjoy it for me. If it is not a cliffhanger, I pray to the Goddess that it blows us away. Adulting is interfering with my AHS.
